# Transient factory runtime state — not committed. The durable, reviewable artifacts
# (PLAN.md, config, schema, _workflow code, agents, verify, reports, findings-graph.json,
# ledger.json, PROGRESS.md, queue) ARE committed; the churn below is regenerable.
state/worktrees/
state/run-args.json
state/items/
state/normalized/
# Runtime markers/leases + --fresh backups (KI-C11 / KI-E6 / setup/init.mjs)
state/controller.json
state/STOP_REQUESTED.md
state/*.pre-fresh-*
# Host-local overrides (KI-E17 / SETUP.md § 6) — per-host, never committed
config/factory.config.local.json
verify/build-test.local.sh
# Telemetry stream (KI-E7 / spine AD-8) — generated event data, never committed
telemetry/data/*
!telemetry/data/.gitkeep
